sources.description:
Humanity Faces The Wrath Of Hell | Angel War | Apocalyptic Fantasy Movie - Gabriel, a retired demon bounty hunter, must return to the dark land when his deceased wife's prophecy comes true that "four angels will come to destroy mankind". He rejoins his former team of demon hunters and finds his estranged best friend Michael harbors a dark secret, the mystical Hannah whose visions predict the future. Gabriel and team must protect this mysterious "fifth" angel from a vicious demon horde.

Angels Fallen | 2020 | Stars: Nicola Posener, Houston Rhines, Michael Teh
